</school>
</conservatory>
</music_school>
, <university wordnetid="108286163" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../941/3088941.xml">
Indiana University</link></university>
.  He studies piano with the program director <weblink xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://info.music.indiana.edu/sb/page/normal/921.html">
Dr. Karen Taylor</weblink>, and music composition with the famous composer <weblink xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://info.music.indiana.edu/sb/page/normal/867.html">
Dr. Don Freund</weblink>.<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%223%22])">3</ref>  Chen's favorite composers are <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../914/17914.xml">
Beethoven</link> and <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../340/99340.xml">
Rachmaninoff</link>. He is also a <championship wordnetid="107457834" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../854/10854.xml">
Formula One</link></championship>
 and <association wordnetid="108049401" confidence="0.8">
<club wordnetid="108227214" confidence="0.8">
<team wordnetid="108208560" confidence="0.8">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../049/15049.xml">
Colts</link></team>
</club>
</association>
 fan.<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%224%22])">4</ref>  </p>

